highlights.text: “愛人錯過” by 告五人 has been on Viral Songs Vietnam the longest, at 221 days straight.
EM XINH "SAY HI" has the most spots on Viral Songs Vietnam. “NGƯỜI ĐẦU TIÊN” is the highest at #8.
“Mưa Sài Gòn Đêm Nay” by TimelessRemixes is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Vietnam at #41.
“From The Start” by neal and Xizt is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Vietnam, up 24 spots at #57.
